  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:36px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:36px;\">獵豹 『北美、上海 國際學校』AMC班課後筆記</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:28px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:26px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><br />\n明天孩子們就要上AMC8考場了！<br />\n<br />\n星媽特地請獵豹提供孩子們考前衝刺的精華講義，這是獵豹 『北美、上海 國際學校』AMC班級的課後筆記，老師考前叮嚀常見解題原則方法，讓孩子上考場能夠完全發揮實力！<br />\n<br />\n獵豹使用講義電子檔，隨時可以放入最新考題，如美國AMC8/10/12、AIME、USAMO、英國UKMT、加拿大Waterloo CEMC、澳洲AMC。例如這份筆記，老師在課堂中就以2021 UKMT考題為例，讓同學掌握最新考題趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n爸爸媽媽們記得轉給孩子看，明天AMC8考場奪得好成績！<br />\n<br />\n另有2022 AMC8直播解題講座回放</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/967973064155379/?__cft__[0]=AZW4yHVr71IUAM5Ff-rFBYgnB6UEFjauzd2X3c5eqw8EC-BIvOSRQD07tv2Tkb3eYJn-TbznDy9Thg12Wcea1unI_o2v1YObzcjqf0LSuJDYsAHkuoQ823GJtcTyZfSbkYVYpZoU2PicgDmL8qxvcB15&amp;__tn__=-UK-R\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/967973064155379/<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong></a><strong>圖文詳見以下臉書連結：</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1217919069160776/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1217919069160776/</a></span></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023080506334699318-f9460d9f.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pi